{"tid":614046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太投入了】睇釘十字架話劇怒打「羅馬兵」 狂漢：我唔會畀耶穌死","createTime":"2018-04-02T07:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T12:19:40.000Z","uid":1121,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"93419ae3a668547c012113e46189d68505d501cc","tid":614046,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"巴西南部一場耶穌受難話劇在復活節演出期間，一名男子突然闖到台上，襲擊飾演羅馬士兵的演員，說要拯救耶穌。<br />\n<br />\n事發於巴西南端南大河州新哈茨（Nova Hartz）市中心。網上流傳的片段顯示，「耶穌」快要被釘十字架時，一名男子突然高喊「我不會讓耶穌死掉」，然後衝上台，在1,000觀眾面前用電單車頭盔兜頭擊向那名「羅馬兵」。演員連忙上前制服施襲者。「羅馬兵」受驚但沒有受傷，事後報警稱遭襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n飾演耶穌的演員在混亂中表現淡定，但導演費雷拉（Adriano Ferreira）為安全起見，一度暫停演出，確保無人受傷後才繼續。<br />\n<br />\n有觀眾表示，最初以為襲擊只是演出一部份，看真一點才知是並非「即興演出」的。<br />\n<br />\n警方就事件展開調查，稱知道施襲者是何許人，指他有精神問題並且濫藥。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》"},{"pid":"07f788593443389d57a8d5d09a050f4ce89c9a09","tid":614046,"uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180402/large/1522608490_8e7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522608490_8e7d.jpg&h=dab5ecb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"143d512ebfffc1b4f7e8392bf8b4140d088d9d55","tid":614046,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"耶撚：<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180402/large/1522608490_8e7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522608490_8e7d.jpg&h=dab5ecb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e7704d934002b197b1da51b7596c3d8a6fb29e7","tid":614046,"uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耶撚：<br />\n<img src=\"http://mypaperimg.pchome.com.tw/newroot2/r/i/rivalshing/content/20050330/23/1246044194.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u